Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.project_titan.model.entity.User

  • public class User
extends Object
    Encapsulates attributes of a single USer. Room and GSON annotations are used to specify entity & attribute mapping for database persistence, and property mapping for JSON serialization/deserialization mapping.
